Power monitoring for HP ZBook Strix Halo

sudo ./ztop.py

We found a fast way to get battery W by reading regs right from the EC

CPU draws about 4W, whole laptop is 7-8W

Unless you turn on the keyboard backlight, that is 2 stupid watts for weak light.




